Suma team manager Victor Mali exuded confidence the charges are well prepared for the opening tie versus Kayole. BF Suma FC have trained sights on dominating the FKF Nairobi East sub-county league ahead of the competition's kick-off this weekend. 

Speaking to Nation Sport, Suma team manager Victor Mali exuded confidence the charges are well prepared for the opening tie versus Kayole. 

"The squad is compact at the moment," he said. 



